Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投不进好球区呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平均球速也只有80公里的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能暂停一会儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里会被踩到  会被压扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别让猫脚玷污了这神圣的操场？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐佐佐佐美！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹濑川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是女子垒球部闪耀的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是校内第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是铃的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓操场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为那些目标崇高  不断挥洒汗水的运动员准备的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是为了你们这些没有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天和猫混在一起的人们所准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且是以比赛为目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是怎么样都行的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话真是怎么样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是在角落里偷玩一下投接球的话也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的忍耐已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们垒球部能够练习  把地方让出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种想法倒是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗铃  你竟敢羞辱我们垒球部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢对佐佐美大人玉足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手冢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许欺负小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来把猫带进操场的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和铃来一对一比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你胜了  我们就从操场离开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是若铃胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要为自己后辈的所作所为道歉  并回去老实练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本小姐怎么可能会输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球  击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的只是陪她玩一下投球练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐美大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,130公里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为猫咪被欺负而认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是紧急关头的怪力一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么重视它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先给刚才的魔球起个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是直球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面寄宿了猫的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷神喵喵球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别闪着星星眼说这话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.94,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(320,332,320,325,0,900)\fad(900,0)}铃习得了雷神喵喵球！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左  右右…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左  右右左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  接下来看谁会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要来吗  手冢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右右左…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经玩过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒娇也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心软了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  是理树啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是信  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次会是什么课题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会收到不可思议的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是第三封了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁出于什么目的送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然写着如果完成全部的课题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会告诉我们世界的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好奇秘密是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治好2-A1号的相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够俗气的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  你知道什么是相思病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思病…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死的病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有人会想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对不对  是说恋爱的相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种病…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是重症吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2-A应该是指班别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号是学号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号应该是男生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过会儿去找找他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找不认识的男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同学和直枝同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是2-A的1号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫相川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子让我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么像坏人来找茬似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一样是二年级  不用这么拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  有啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  这种话不能说出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在患有相思病  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用多说  我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事前早有调查过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有调查过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当我有眼线就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  你有什么症状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们替你治好这个病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来也会轻松一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我们会保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  请别跟其他人说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她在我面前  这里就揪心的痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习也学不进去  上课时满脑子都是她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这是初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习运动文武双全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还很有人望  是个很厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的人完全配不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说还真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  还没向她告白的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告白什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是失败会很悲惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所作为就放弃不会更懊悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  对方是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  知道对方是谁也方便我们提建议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…笹濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里听到她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是你问我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我没有问那家伙的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  你是问了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  也就是说相川君的心上人是笹濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  这到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  平静下来  冷静想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是呐  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越是想要冷静就越是会混乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  他不是说那人学习运动文武双全还很有人望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所知道的佐佐佐佐佐美可不是那样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不能现在去破坏他的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的问题不在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你们还挺配的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身后不是总跟着几个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定能成为其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是只能当朋友的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  应该比这更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我跟她挺熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能给你们牵个线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连理树也在惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备如何去给他们牵线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿要在我房间开个茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想邀请小铃也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  我觉得能听到不少主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬  我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚决不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能自己吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么听话地过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我十分高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想问问大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽管问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…如何才能…两情相悦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃有心上人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜蜜蜜的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是谁  是大姐姐我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说我  是让其他人两情相悦的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同学和恭介同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们之间有着深深的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围的人不用特意去为他们操心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如说操心反而会打扰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是在图书馆里伸手想要拿同一本书的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人大喊着要迟到了要迟到了在拐角撞一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱便开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混进去不少乱七八糟的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树觉得怎么做比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问问她的爱好和喜欢的类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问了之后怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是告诉相川君啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他应该很想更多地了解自己的心上人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗铃  从刚才开始一直叽叽咕咕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话先说在前头  之前那事没门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  话说回来你有什么爱好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末的时候在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就问了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问这些东西有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想要拿来当作我的笑柄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是拿来当笑柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  想更深地了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能更加亲密一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与叫佐濑川佐佐美的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:11:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是在耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想要问什么来着  爱好和什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末你都在做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有理想中的男生是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外貌啊性格之类的  希望你能详细地告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末要练习垒球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想中的男士是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑道部的宫泽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渣渣美她喜欢谦吾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么去和相川君说  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先问问谦吾他怎么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就到这地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么一回事  你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我怎么看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前  你认识笹濑川同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识倒是认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么的总是会在走廊里和她碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都会和我打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她倒是在试着接近谦吾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我怎么回答才能让你们结束这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是「我没那个意思」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样满意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾他没那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫泽同学他怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是有关笹濑川同学的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说喜欢的对象是谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  他好像受了不小的打击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说他身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明显是前者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是大惊小怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾他没那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对你来说不正好是个机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说谦吾的魅力是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先试着考虑一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾虽然块头很大很吓人  对人也不怎么亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的魅力就是他的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解释成很有男子汉气概的话也还行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒谦吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够跳跃的思维
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在渣渣美面前把那个强大的谦吾给打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就一定会迷上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不怎么运动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是打不赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就培养相同的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川同学不是没什么爱好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要提一些可能相同的爱好就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画和游戏之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去不太能和她相同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐之类的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么经常听的音乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hip Hop吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Desktop电脑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个音是相同的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借她几张你喜欢的CD如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就借CD？  难度也太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就唱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在原创的歌词之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐含着对渣渣美秘密的爱慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的那句歌词记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「笹濑川佐佐美  就是你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  Mission Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey you hey you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You you come on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Check it  现在  check it  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半吊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有挽回的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒谦吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  我是打不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  不偷袭的话确实打不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点卑鄙  也只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此  还是感觉打不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就来个偷袭乘3吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘3？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我假装摔倒  滑到谦吾的脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  谦吾一定会跳着躲开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是理树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴里说着「A套餐久等了」把餐盘砸向谦吾的后脑勺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样他一定会抱着头蹲在地上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时你就一边大喊「宫泽谦吾受死吧」一边一脚踢上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就算踢一脚上去也没什么用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就使尽浑身解数冲过去踢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从两百米开外助跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这走廊还真够长的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去撞他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定没办法躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲过去的话肯定能把他撞飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被撞飞的样子  可是相当难见到一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定很具有冲击性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会成为传说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐美来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A套餐久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相川君  不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫泽谦吾  受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么新玩法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是恭介那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个伤脑筋的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有歹人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  是刚才那个失礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到事情的部分经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是宫泽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…宫泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次会再考虑得周到一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们帮我这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  你有谈过恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得之所以会失败是因为我们没经历过恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱不是幸福的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是很痛苦的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如其名  就像是疾病一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要放弃却无法放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:17:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会一直痛苦下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的指令是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治好相思病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没写要成全他俩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要硬去撮合他俩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要治好他单相思的痛苦就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三番五次地到底是想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部？  那个失礼的家伙也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你能原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  能…能把你的邮箱地址告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想要和我成为朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是另外一个人想要和你成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他直接来和我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙一看到你就会揪心的痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会经常想你每天在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满脑子里都是你  学习也学不进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我不太明白这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家伙  看起来真的很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑…渣渣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「心痛」的感觉我倒是能够体会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿手机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹来川渣渣美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹濑川佐佐美！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是佐佐美的邮箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是每天只能发一封哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多的话要等你们关系更近一些后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后除了发邮件以外  尽量别去一直想她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习也给我好好去学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就算是解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就看他的表现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过铃你已经把能做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃有朝一日会不会也喜欢上别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球速变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再把猫咪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许欺负小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还什么都没干…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笹濑佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笹濑川佐佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不也咬到舌头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  又来闹事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事情想问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我宫泽大人喜欢吃什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真有女人缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉她是「不倒汤直接吃的速食炒面」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒汤直接吃的速食炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒汤真是太环保了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样会是怎样的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有吃过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没吃过  再说这是真人骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我今天一定要把你的那张贫嘴给封上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.10,up,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.08,up,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星空之下  我参加了库特那不可思议的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树有看到过南十字星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特那不为人知的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正浮出水面
